# Common patterns for all middleware projects

# Dependencies
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-lock.yaml
**/.pnpm-debug.log*

# Build output
**/dist/
**/build/
**/out/
**/.next/
**/.nuxt/

# IDE
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/.DS_Store

# Environment variables
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Testing
**/coverage/
**/.nyc_output/

# Logs
**/logs/
**/*.log

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Temporary files
**/*.tmp
**/*.temp
**/.cache/

# TypeScript
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Package managers
.yarn/
.pnpm-store/